### II.2 Epistemological Clarity

**Status:** ✅ **RESOLVED**

The Olympian Standard v2.3 and `MASTER_REVISED_APPROACH.veth` now clearly distinguish:

| Tier | Definition | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| **Proven** | Follows from axioms; computationally verified | 93, 171, 156, 42, 12.37%, 5 gaps |
| **Internal** | Emerges from system computations; valid within system rules | Beat frequency 0.6607, overpack delta |
| **Interpretive** | Maps system structures to physical phenomena; not causal | 13-node lattice as $m_\ell$ model |
| **Speculative** | Proposes physical mechanisms without derivation | 66 Hz harmonic emission, 93 as nuclear limit |

